PRIVACY POLICY
Introduction
The Testline App and its affiliates (“we”, “our” or “us”) believe that your privacy is important. Protecting your private information is our priority. This Privacy Policy explains how we do collection of data, its usage and sharing of information, including personally identifiable information when you use our app (The Testline App) or our website (www.testline.in), which are collectively referred to as “Services”. By using our Services, you consent to the data practices described in this policy.
Please review this Privacy Policy carefully. If you do not agree with any of its terms, please do not use our app and/or request the deletion of your personal information from our records.
Your continued use of our website will be regarded as acceptance
of our practices around privacy and personal information. If you have any questions about how we handle user data and personal information, feel free to contact us.
Third Party Service Providers
To provide you with the best Services possible, we also use third party service providers, which we entrust storing data, its collection and analysis. We believe that all third party service providers are important to our effective operation. They have their own Privacy Policies and their own conditions, whether to collect your data or opt-out from it.
                    Please be aware that we have no control over the content and practices of these sites, and cannot accept responsibility or liability for their respective privacy policies.
We provide the information on these services and links to their respective Privacy Policies:
Firebase — https://www.firebase.com/terms/privacy-policy.html
Segment - https://segment.com/docs/legal/privacy/
Amplitude - https://amplitude.com/privacy
Information we collect from you
We may collect personally identifiable information, such as your name and email address. We may also collect anonymous demographic information, which is not unique to you, such as your age. We may gather additional personal and non-personal information in the future. This information you actively provide to us.
